data.description: Charming 2 Bedroom Brick House in Greenbrier, Embrace the warmth of this inviting 2-bedroom, 1-bath brick home nestled on a generous 0.5-acre lot. This home is the epitome of comfort, combining classic charm with modern amenities. Enjoy the cozy ambiance of a crackling fireplace, creating the ideal setting for memorable moments with family and friends during chilly evenings. The glass-enclosed porch provides a serene space to enjoy the changing seasons, rain or shine. Shield your vehicles from the elements with a convenient carport, ensuring protection and easy access year-round. Solid brick construction not only aesthetically pleasing but also built to stand the test of time. The enduring charm of brick adds a timeless quality to the property. The spacious lot provides endless possibilities for gardening, outdoor activities, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Rest easy knowing that the home boasts a newer roof, providing both durability and peace of mind. Don't miss this opportunity.
